sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant JOB as Scheduler / PriceUpdate
    participant ALS as AlertService
    participant REP as PriceAlertRepository
    participant EVT as Kafka
    participant MAIL as EmailService
    participant UI as Frontend

    JOB->>ALS: checkAlertsForSymbol(symbol, currentPrice)
    ALS->>REP: Aktif alarmlari getir
    REP-->>ALS: Alarm listesi
    ALS->>ALS: shouldTrigger kurallari
    ALS->>REP: Trigger + persist
    ALS->>EVT: Notification event publish
    ALS->>MAIL: E-posta gonder
    ALS-->>UI: Anlik bildirim
